name: FBI Hacked Me
description:
The FBI is trying to hack your computer...

You have 30 seconds to delete as many files as possible. Be careful though, you lose points for deleting unnecessary files. Read the file names and try to figure out which ones to delete. Click and drag them to the trash can on the bottom left.

Once you have deleted as many as you think you can, click the scrubber on the bottom right before the timer runs out.

If the timer runs out before you click the scrubber, you lose.
